g(z)=\frac{f(z)-f(z_0)}{z-z_0}
z \in \Delta(z_0,r)\setminus\{z_0\}.
0< \rho < r
\left| g(z) \right|=\max\limits_{|z|=\rho}\left|g(z)\right|=\max\limits_{|z|=\rho}\left|\frac{f(z)-f(z_0)}{z-z_0}\right|\leq \frac{m}{r}.
